%% LM Evaluation Harness - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval Operator
    participant Job as LMES Job Container<br/>UBI9 Python 3.11<br/>User: 65532
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Inference Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3-Compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>5000/TCP

    Operator->>Job: Create Kubernetes Job<br/>Mount /meta/job.json ConfigMap

    Note over Job: Read job.json specification

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token

    opt S3 Model Asset Download
        Job->>S3: GET model assets/datasets<br/>TLS 1.2+ / AWS IAM
        S3-->>Job: Model weights, tokenizer files
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: LOADING_DATA<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token

    Note over Job: Load benchmark tasks<br/>Configure evaluation parameters

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: RUNNING_EVALUATION<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token

    loop For each evaluation prompt batch
        Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)
        Model-->>Job: Model completions response
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token

    Note over Job: Compute metrics and scores

    opt OCI Artifact Export
        Job->>OCI: Push evaluation results artifact<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Docker auth
        OCI-->>Job: Push confirmation
    end

    opt MLflow Logging
        Job->>MLflow: POST metrics, parameters, artifacts<br/>HTTP/HTTPS / Configurable auth
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: COMPLETED<br/>Results: metrics, scores, duration<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Bearer Token
